text: waited almost an hour for my food, just for them to have forgotten my order. asked for a refund and miraculously the order immediately comes out. could do better in terms of service and waiting times.
Takes an infinite amount to service. By the time your food arrives, you no longer want to eat. The quality is good though. But I hate the longer wait time.
This Co-op shop is promoting products created by students and alumni.
Only students and staff can go in. Co-op very small, nothing much in there.
Quite a small shop, but love the services provided!
